Richard Allen &lt;roborick007@...&gt; wrote:: : Kup : :

At first Kup was startled when the tree was shattered but he was put at ease once he saw the newcomers insignia. He was the same as Kup, a Autobot.

Kup: Welcome to Earth of the past, lad. I&#39;m Kup and this is Windlord. I&#39;m sure we can find a place for you at our Maximal base. It&#39;s a bit of a mess right now do to some un-friendly dealings, but it&#39;s a place.


robert riley &lt;bustercross365@...&gt; wrote:
The bounty hunter lashed at a tree, reducing it to splinters.  He slowly stepped out of the shade, and walked with his flank to Kup and Windlord, so they could see the black and gold Autobot insignia.  He then turned and transformed into his robot mode and addressed the Maximal and Autobot.
&quot;I am Malice.  I&#39;m a bounty hunter.  I crashed a while ago, my prey is somewhere on this planet.  I, regretfully, need a place to stay.&quot;

Richard Allen &lt;roborick007@...&gt; wrote:
: : Kup : :

Kup pulled up alongside Windlord, transforming to bot mode.

Kup: I see you responded to. Good. We dont know what we&#39;re dealing with yet.


